    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "exactly. a liability. and the more I try to fix it, the more it breaks. it feels like there is no way to actually win here. it just feels like the only way to actually stop the bleeding and let them breathe is if i just... stopped being a factor in the equation entirely. like, wouldn't it be more logical if they could just move forward without me holding them back?",
